Direct Fixed - Fixed directly with no cavity.
Monolithic - Smooth rendered plaster finish over a selected substrate.
Vermin Strip - Strip used to allow airflow but stop rodents accessing.
Soffits - Overhanging horizontal lining under the overhanging roof.
Eaves - Pitched section of roof overhang.
